result.name: Lau Sum Kee Noodle

reviews.text: Great goose and rice dishes for very affordable prices. The service was quick and food is tasty. Cleanliness wise, I would not leave my belongings on the ground as it is very greasy. Seating is fairly large however do expect a lineup during afternoon tea.

Little place fills up easily, especially at meal times.  There maybe a line outside waiting for seats, however it does move fast as people don't generally stay long.  Be prepared to share your table with others.
Known for shrimp roe noodles which are always a great choice.  Have some of the free pickled turnip in the jar in middle of the table, while waiting for the noodles to arrive.

The soup noodles are more tasty than the dry one. The wanton noodles are very tasty. Don't forget to eat the preserved white radish in the glass jar. It's more tasty than it looks! Goes well with the noodles!
Tiny but cozy place. Of course, foods are good.

reviews.text: Small local shopping centre; choices are limited
there are plenty trading card game shops, if you are a fan of card game, you should come here to have alook
Look for cards and figures? There's plenty! You will find a few shops selling antiques as well
The address is wrong, waste of time.

a very local shopping mall, no well known fashion brand, not selling range of service. with lots of card games shop, with tutorial center and catering. 
you can find Chinese restaurant at upper floor. mainly serving senior group. 
comparatively the plaza design is quite old. elevator available for going up, you need to walk when going downstairs.

reviews.text:
香港集玩卡牌遊戲的集中地，有不少同類型的店家。能找到不同TCG的商品，及有機會跟其他玩家對戰。
商場環境較為老化，偶有滴水或中央空調失靈的情況。商場大約每天晚上10點左右關閉中央空調，環境會較為悶熱。

商場的結構，尤如“8”字的鏡射設計，初次到來的人，會比較容易迷失方向。
於商場1樓，分別設有1條通往商場2樓的扶手電梯，以及另一條通往酒樓的扶手電梯。（※附上商場地圖，及2條扶手電梯的照片供參考用）
附帶一提，下樓只有樓梯可以用。
